tanqeed Test 13: Scope

rakho x = 100

banao inner () ->
  tanqeed x from outer scope is visible here
  dikhao x
  rakho y = 999
  tanqeed y only lives inside this function
end

bulao inner
tanqeed y is gone now - the next line would crash if uncommented
tanqeed dikhao y

tanqeed Outer x is unchanged
dikhao x